<br />There are translations and hacks of Mega Man 2, which means <em>somebody</em> knows something about how it works. <a href="http://www.datacrystal.org/wiki/Mega_Man_2" class="postlink">DataCrystal.org has the beginning of a ROM and RAM map</a>. We could start by trying to plug the MM9 levels into MM2's <a href="http://www.romhacking.net/?category=&amp;Platform=&amp;game=795&amp;author=&amp;os=&amp;level=&amp;perpage=20&amp;page=utilities&amp;utilsearch=Go&amp;title=&amp;desc=" class="postlink">level editor</a>.

		

