<br />
<br />Don't get me wrong, I'm not lazy and would TOTALLY do this if I knew how. But before I learn something like 6502, I want to see if someone who already knows it is willing to undertake this. Learning 6502 AND porting MM9 to NES all by myself would take years.

		

